@@TJvVisualId3v1.LoadFromFile@string
Description:
Use this method to load the tag from a file. You can also set FileName property, it has the same effect.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvVisualId3v1.RemoveTagFromFile@string
Description:
Use this method to remove an id3v1 tag from a file. if the tag isn't present, it has no effect, and if the tag is present, it's removed.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvVisualId3v1.SaveToFile@string
Description:
Use this method to save the tag to a FileName. if a tag is already present in the file, the tag is modified. if no tag is present, a new tag is appened.

